text:
Boss is friendly. Dart n pool table available wif Karaoke. Typical KTV pub.
HH till 9pm.
Didn't grade food with more starts as it's not their in house food. But they dun mind if we bring our own nuts n chips.
Love the place, with ktv, darts and pool. Great atmosphere with good sound systems. There's food menu to order food and can buy nuts/tidbits from outside and bring in

seen this joint around for a long time, especially if you drive.

friend jio last min and I was like okay, let's go, but abit apprehensive because I was under the impression the crowd more mature.

end up, it was really chill, family like experience, mixed of young and not so young, can order food (2 page mind you!) from the tze char downstairs which was great!

The passage way towards the toilet was full of smokers, despite in the building. Smokers crowding around a dustbin blowing the air out from a small window but but is really bad for non smokers when you need to use the toilet.
Sound system is good, the microphone was very compensating and catches your voice easily.
The waitress kept chasing you to drink. Had even took my beer for my friendâ€™s next table and they pour out so many glasses for nothing. Rude and no etiquette.
Avoid at all costs

Pricey for a KTV pub. $12 for a glass of coke is ridiculous. Ordered a tower of beer as well and it's obvious that it has been watered down. Basically a good place to play pool, darts and sing but you'll be sorely disappointed if you are seeking value from their beverage.
